;nbsp; 17: Ancient Set&amp;nbsp; 18: Salvager Set&amp;nbsp; 19: Hero Of Wild Set&amp;nbsp; 20: Dark Set&amp;nbsp; 21: Fierce Deity Set 22: Soldier's Set&amp;nbsp; 23: Snowquill Set&amp;nbsp; 24: Royal Guard Set&amp;nbsp; 25: Phantom Ganon Set.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hylian Hood's A and B are switched depending on the upper armor.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;[ Individual Selection Ver ]&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This version allows you to select all armors except the default one. You can also change the default hairstyle.&lt;br&gt;There are 8 bnp files packed in the zip file, so please choose one and install it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Additional armor for NudeLink V2.0.1 [&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/536202"&gt;Honey Bee Link&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;If you have any problems using this mod, please report them in the comments section. (We may not be able to address all of them...)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Please select one of the files below to install. Select each option in the BCML installation window.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
