      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66e6ff6208816.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66e6ff6c1d64d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a compilation of memory fixes for various Zelda mods, allowing you to load them at the same time as other large mods&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Fixes crashes when combining Zelda mods with mods like Second Wind, Relics of the Past, and Dark Army&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Install with BCML, or, for even more stability, migrate to &lt;a href="https://github.com/GingerAvalanche/ukmm/releases/tag/v0.15.0" target="_blank"&gt;this version of UKMM&lt;/a&gt; (or any newer, official version) and install this mod with it to eliminate ALL panic moons!*&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Note: I haven't tried to install the bnp with UKMM. UKMM installs the original file I created just fine, but the original file also adds an actor info entry for each of Second Wind's custom armor upgrades, which means that if Second Wind ever decides to update those, the UKMM zip download version of this mod will override those changes. The bnp has been directly edited so that *only* the instSizes are present in it, but UKMM might not like installing it if Second Wind is not also installed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;tl;dr- Install the bnp version, even with UKMM. If you get an error when installing the bnp version, only then should you try the UKMM zip version.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also note that this contains no assets from Zelda's Ballad. It's, essentially, a collection of numbers that Zelda's Ballad was missing (because we didn't know how to find them when ZB was made). The bnp contains no data from other mods, and the UKMM zip contains a small amount of data from Second Wind.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;*That I have been able to find&lt;br&gt;</description>
