    <item>
      <title>Renamed Amiibo Gear</title>
      <author>Chalmoro Azohen</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/459740</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/459740#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">4d99187d03f641b49463a3479c20361e001869fa</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 22:37:42 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64c82afb47878.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64c82b087b205.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Adding the Rest&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;I decided to add options for all of the changes. I tried to make everything optional, but BCML wasn't playing nice, so the Sword of the Hero is mandatory in the BNP. Sorry for anyone who happened to &lt;em&gt;not&lt;/em&gt; want that one changed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added options&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;It always bugged me that the Zelda 1 sword was just called "Sword," and it gets a bit weird when you have multiple mods with shields called "Hero's Shield." Thus, I was quite pleased when the corresponding sword and shield were renamed "Sword of the Hero" and "Sea-Breeze Shield" in Tears of the Kingdom. I like that, so I edited them in Breath of the Wild. I suppose I &lt;i&gt;could&lt;/i&gt; have made the other amiibo gear names match the ones in TotK, but I prefer them as-is, like how "Scimitar of the Seven" is cooler then "Dusk Claymore" in my opinion. Options for the other changes have been added now.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For those curious, I copied the Actors (Weapon_Sword_58 and Weapon_Shield_57) from the game files and used the BotW Actor Tool to change the name before sticking them in a folder for the mod. For some reason, the name isn't universally changed, as the memory editor I have that can edit things while the game is running still refers to them as "Sword" and "Hero's Shield," but that's not a major issue.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/totkamiibogearrename_b8cf9.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <category>Weapons</category>
      <category>Skins</category>
    </item>
